    
Space Complexity:
Count how much extra memory you use as input grows.

Pattern	                              SC
No extra storage	                    O(1)
Storing n elements (array, map, list)	O(n)
Storing n² elements	                  O(n²)


Simple rule of thumb:
* Look at your loops for time complexity
* Look at your data structures for space complexity

Time Complexity:
Count how many times your code repeats work as input grows.
Pattern	                           TC
Single loop	                       O(n)
Nested loop	                       O(n²)
Loop inside loop inside loop	     O(n³)
No loop, just statements           O(1) 

Cutting input in half 
each step (binary search)          O(log n)
